n>105<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> It surpassed <i><a hre=
f=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lost_in_Space_(film)" title=3D"Lost in S=
pace (film)">Lost in Space</a></i> and <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Indecent_Proposal" title=3D"Indecent Proposal">Indecent Proposal</a=
></i> simultaneously for having the biggest April and <a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Easter" title=3D"Easter">Easter</a> opening weekends.<s=
