lm, trailing behind <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liar_Liar" =
title=3D"Liar Liar">Liar Liar</a></i>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-ShowsMuscle_106-2=
" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Matrix#c=
ite_note-ShowsMuscle-106"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>105<span cla=
ss=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> Three years later in 2002, <i>The Ma=
trix</i><span class=3D"nowrap" style=3D"padding-left:0.1em;">'</span>s reco=
rds for having the largest April and Easter opening weekends would be taken=
 by <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Scorpion_King" title=3D=
