https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Payback_(1999_film)" title=3D"Payback (1999 f=
ilm)">Payback</a></i>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-ShowsMuscle_106-3" class=3D"refer=
ence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Matrix#cite_note-ShowsMu=
scle-106"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>105<span class=3D"cite-brack=
et">]</span></a></sup> Additionally, this was the biggest opening weekend f=
or a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keanu_Reeves" title=3D"Keanu =
Reeves">Keanu Reeves</a> film since <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/=
wiki/Speed_(1994_film)" title=3D"Speed (1994 film)">Speed</a></i> in 1994.<=
sup id=3D"cite_ref-109" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia=
.org/wiki/The_Matrix#cite_note-109"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>10=
8<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> It would go on to rank num=
ber one at the box office during its first weekend, beating out <i><a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forces_of_Nature_(1999_film)" title=3D"Fo=
