<p><i>The Matrix</i> received <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acad=
emy_Awards" title=3D"Academy Awards">Academy Awards</a> for <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Film_Editing" title=3D"Aca=
demy Award for Best Film Editing">Best Film Editing</a>, Best Sound Editing=
, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Visual_Ef=
fects" title=3D"Academy Award for Best Visual Effects">Best Visual Effects<=
/a> and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Sou=
nd" title=3D"Academy Award for Best Sound">Best Sound</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_r=
ef-133" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Ma=
trix#cite_note-133"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>132<span class=3D"=
cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-134" class=3D"reference=
"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Matrix#cite_note-134"><span =
class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>133<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a>=
</sup> The filmmakers were competing against other films with established f=
ranchises, like <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars:_Epis=
ode_I_%E2%80%93_The_Phantom_Menace" title=3D"Star Wars: Episode I =E2=80=93=
 The Phantom Menace">Star Wars: Episode I =E2=80=93 The Phantom Menace</a><=
/i>, yet they won all four of their nominations.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Oscars2=
000_135-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The=
_Matrix#cite_note-Oscars2000-135"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>134<=
span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-oscars2_1=
36-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Matr=
ix#cite_note-oscars2-136"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>135<span cla=
ss=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> <i>The Matrix</i> also received <a h=
ref=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAFTA" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"=
BAFTA">BAFTA</a> awards for <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAFTA_=
Award_for_Best_Sound" title=3D"BAFTA Award for Best Sound">Best Sound</a> a=
nd <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAFTA_Award_for_Best_Special_Vi=
sual_Effects" title=3D"BAFTA Award for Best Special Visual Effects">Best Ac=
hievement in Special Visual Effects</a>, in addition to nominations in the =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAFTA_Award_for_Best_Cinematograph=
y" title=3D"BAFTA Award for Best Cinematography">cinematography</a>, <a hre=
f=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAFTA_Award_for_Best_Production_Design" =
title=3D"BAFTA Award for Best Production Design">production design</a> and =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAFTA_Award_for_Best_Editing" titl=
e=3D"BAFTA Award for Best Editing">editing</a> categories.<sup id=3D"cite_r=
ef-baftas_137-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/The_Matrix#cite_note-baftas-137"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>13=
6<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> In 1999, it won <a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saturn_Awards" title=3D"Saturn Awards">Satur=
n Awards</a> for <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saturn_Award_for_=
Best_Science_Fiction_Film" title=3D"Saturn Award for Best Science Fiction F=
ilm">Best Science Fiction Film</a> and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/=
wiki/Saturn_Award_for_Best_Director" title=3D"Saturn Award for Best Directo=
r">Best Direction</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Saturn_Award_138-0" class=3D"refe=
rence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Matrix#cite_note-Saturn=
_Award-138"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>137<span class=3D"cite-bra=
cket">]</span></a></sup> In February 2022, the film was named one of the fi=
ve finalists for Oscars Cheer Moment as part of the <a href=3D"https://en.w=
ikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts_and_Sciences" title=3D"Aca=
demy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences">Academy of Motion Picture Arts an=
d Sciences</a>' "<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oscars_Fan_Favori=
te" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Oscars Fan Favorite">Oscars Fan Favorite=
</a>" contest, for the "bullet time" scene, finishing in fifth place.<sup i=
d=3D"cite_ref-139" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/=
wiki/The_Matrix#cite_note-139"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>138<spa=
n class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-140" class=
=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Matrix#cite_not=
e-140"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>139<span class=3D"cite-bracket"=
>]</span></a></sup>
</p>
